{"id": "1427270864864280606", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "ありがとうございます〜\nすみません。ざっと調べた限りだと、カレンとオレッタの入手場所が分からなかったのですが、どこで加入するキャラでしょうか…？", "timestamp": "2025-10-13T12:24:51.594000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1427268978367266858", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1427271955790168144", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "1134504454738157669", "author_name": "shachi1019", "author_bot": false, "content": "闇の境界線任務というもので入手できます〜。イベント欄にあると思います", "timestamp": "2025-10-13T12:29:11.691000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["516998769888329749"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1427270864864280606", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1427272732273278977", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "了解です！進めてみますー", "timestamp": "2025-10-13T12:32:16.819000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1427271955790168144", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
